{"tid":307544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★獨居中年男，死後3日發臭被揭發！","createTime":"2017-07-03T12:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T12:55:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f6502f5545942d3363cc1ae13ce5a37fac7e77d2","tid":307544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:38:11.000Z","msg":"大埔泮涌路舊泮涌村，獨居漢被揭猝死。早上8時45分，上址一間村屋傳出難聞氣味，街坊感到可疑，拍門無人回應，且未能聯絡上獨居的姓高男戶主(46歲)，遂通知其54歲兄長到場察看，其兄接獲通知後趕至，見大門虛掩，恐有意外發生，於是報案。<br />\n<br />\n估計死去至少3日，經調查後，得悉高患有心臟病，初步懷疑他因病猝死，相信事件無可疑，案件列作發現屍體，其死因有待驗屍後確定。至下午2時許，死者遺體由仵工舁送殮房。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，高無業，以往與父母及4兄弟姊妹同住上址，及後眾人陸續遷出，只剩高獨居。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170703/bkn-20170703105059587-0703_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170703%2Fbkn-20170703105059587-0703_00822_001.html&d=PP%2B4JVT6z9V4CN2Chq47FZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6bb31f5e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170703/bkn-20170703105059587-0703_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"31f4cedd503439055cf7bde5307d25bf47834690","tid":307544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:38:36.000Z","msg":"邊位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31c825670854544871f18aec2cc9517a26c6e64","tid":307544,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4c95c914ec80c06a0010dfe3831a827df30e33","tid":307544,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:39:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b46d298f9d85dd71f76362fabcbca1e2d80a94b3","tid":307544,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T12:42:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 